WEBVTT

00:00:58.292 --> 00:01:00.958
She smiled innocently and said no.

00:01:01.875 --> 00:01:06.184
But deep down, I was sure
she wanted to give it a try.

00:01:06.208 --> 00:01:09.434
With a little bit of perseverance
and a lot of effort,

00:01:09.458 --> 00:01:11.268
we managed to write her name.

00:01:11.292 --> 00:01:15.208
Her hands were trembling,
and her face was beaming with pride.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.893
As I watched her do this,

00:01:18.917 --> 00:01:21.518
for the first time in my life,

00:01:21.542 --> 00:01:24.643
I had a priceless feeling:

00:01:24.667 --> 00:01:28.208
that I could be of some use to this world.